      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, what? sorry, i think there was a typo in your last message or something? i'm not sure what you meant by the part about a goblin. anyway, regarding the meeting thing, what if they refuse to acknowledge the impact on the team and just keep making excuses? how do i escalate this without it looking like i'm just picking sides?",
